content: स्नु {c2c} <ab>P.</ab> (स्नौति, स्नुत) {@--1@} To drip, trickle, fall in drops, distil, drop, ooze or run out, leak out. {@--2@} To flow, stream.

स्नु {%<ab>m.</ab>%} {%<ab>n.</ab>%} {@--1@} Table-land. {@--2@} Top, surface (in general). (This word has no forms for the first five inflections and is optionally substituted for सानु after <ab>acc.</ab> dual).
